    "title": "Immediate Requirement Store Manager at Zara India Digital Technologies",
    "description": "Grow your career with Zara India Digital Technologies! We are hiring a Store Manager for our Navi Mumbai team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Zara India Digital Technologies:\nZara India Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in CRM\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zara India Digital Technologies!",
